<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/19771811">如何翻译《What A Wonderful World》的歌词？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="88801" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"> I see trees of green, red roses too<br>I see them bloom for me and you<br>And I think to myself what a wonderful world.<br><br>I see skies of blue and clouds of white<br>The bright blessed days, the dark sacred nights<br>And I think to myself what a wonderful world.<br><br>The colors of the rainbow so pretty in the sky<br>Are also on the faces of people going by<br>I see friends shaking hands saying how do you do<br>They're really saying I love you.<br><br>I hear babies cry, I watch them grow<br>They'll learn much more than I'll never know<br>And I think to myself what a wonderful world<br>Yes I think to myself what a wonderful world. <br><br>要合折押韵，节奏感也和原作契合。不必逐字直译，意境更加重要。 </div>


</div>
